20171227 114521.379 UPDATE t
20171227 114521.379 SET <f:t.ContraAcc> = CASE WHEN <f:e.DebtorId> is NOT null AND <f:e.DebtorId> <<>> '' THEN <f:e.DebtorId> ELSE CASE WHEN <f:e.CreditorId> is NOT null AND <f:e.CreditorId> <<>> ''  THEN <f:e.CreditorId> ELSE <f:e.LedgerId> END END,
20171227 114521.379 <f:t.ContraAccType> = CASE WHEN <f:e.DebtorId> is NOT null THEN 'D' ELSE CASE WHEN <f:e.CreditorId> is NOT null THEN 'K' ELSE 'S' END END

20171227 114532.805 SET <f:ForwardBalance> =

20171227 114532.805       NULL 
20171227 114532.805    ELSE 
20171227 114532.805       ISNULL(<f:ForwardDebit>, 0) - ISNULL(<f:ForwardCredit>, 0)
20171227 114532.805    END
20171227 114532.805 ,<f:PrePeriods> = 
20171227 114532.805    CASE WHEN <f:PrePeriodsDebit> IS NULL AND <f:PrePeriodsCredit> IS NULL THEN 
20171227 114532.805       NULL 
20171227 114532.805    ELSE 
20171227 114532.805       ISNULL(<f:PrePeriodsDebit>, 0) - ISNULL(<f:PrePeriodsCredit>, 0) 
20171227 114532.805    END
20171227 114532.805 , <f:ForwardPreBalance> = 
20171227 114532.805    CASE WHEN <f:ForwardDebit> IS NULL AND <f:ForwardCredit> IS NULL AND <f:PrePeriodsDebit> IS NULL AND <f:PrePeriodsCredit> IS NULL THEN 
20171227 114532.805       NULL 
20171227 114532.805    ELSE 
20171227 114532.805       ISNULL(<f:ForwardDebit>, 0) - ISNULL(<f:ForwardCredit>, 0) + ISNULL(<f:PrePeriodsDebit>, 0) - ISNULL(<f:PrePeriodsCredit>, 0) 
20171227 114532.805    END
20171227 114532.805 , <f:ForwardPreDebit> = 
20171227 114532.805    CASE WHEN <f:ForwardDebit> IS NULL AND <f:PrePeriodsDebit> IS NULL THEN 
20171227 114532.805       NULL 
20171227 114532.805    ELSE 
20171227 114532.806       ISNULL(<f:ForwardDebit>, 0) + ISNULL(<f:PrePeriodsDebit>, 0)
20171227 114532.806    END
20171227 114532.806 , <f:ForwardPreCredit> = 
20171227 114532.806    CASE WHEN <f:ForwardCredit> IS NULL AND <f:PrePeriodsCredit> IS NULL THEN 
20171227 114532.806       NULL 
20171227 114532.806    ELSE 
20171227 114532.806       ISNULL(<f:ForwardCredit>, 0) + ISNULL(<f:PrePeriodsCredit>, 0)
20171227 114532.806    END
20171227 114532.806 , <f:PreCurrentBalance> = 
20171227 114532.806    CASE WHEN <f:PrePeriodsDebit> IS NULL AND <f:PrePeriodsCredit> IS NULL AND <f:ValueDebit> IS NULL AND <f:ValueCredit> IS NULL THEN 
20171227 114532.806       NULL

20171227 114532.806    END
20171227 114532.806 , <f:PreCurrentDebit> =
